longBusinessSummary: Cinis Fertilizer AB (publ), a green tech company, produces and sells mineral fertilizers by recycling industrial waste products in Sweden. The company offers water soluble sulfate of potash by upcycling waste products from the pulp and paper industry, and the electric vehicle battery industry. It also provides fossil-free sodium chloride as a byproduct. Cinis Fertilizer AB (publ) was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Örnsköldsvik, Sweden.
